      <title>hexo博客的搭建教程</title>
      <link href="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="hexo博客的搭建"><a href="#hexo博客的搭建" class="headerlink" title="==hexo博客的搭建=="></a>==hexo博客的搭建==</h2><p>为了记录自身成长 决定搭建一个博客，本来想着选择一个博客项目自己搭建放在服务器上进行写作，后来了解到有hexo框架进行一体式操作直接生成简单方便，而且可以挂在GitHub上 省时省事省心</p><p>官网：<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/</a></p><h4 id="安装好环境"><a href="#安装好环境" class="headerlink" title="安装好环境"></a>安装好环境</h4><ol><li><p>node.js</p><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/">https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/</a></p><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820131742697.png" alt="image-20210820131742697"></p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820131742697.png" class="" title="This is an example image"><p>下载稳定版就行了  下载完后一直点击确定安装就好了</p><p>安装成功后可能需要==配置好环境变量跟系统变量还有全局设置== 这些可以百度到，这里就不再缀叙了。不过这里很重要==因为这里我没设置好 虽然可以查出node跟npm的版本 但是压根就用不了 安装不了其他东西== </p></li><li><p>git</p><p><a href="https://git-scm.com/">https://git-scm.com/</a></p><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820132206915.png" alt="image-20210820132206915"></p><p>直接下载也是一直点确定到底就行</p></li></ol><p>​       ==这里记得去百度git初始化 登录好邮箱跟用户名不然等下上传到GitHub的时候会报错==这里就不多做说明。</p><h4 id="进行-hexo-的安装"><a href="#进行-hexo-的安装" class="headerlink" title="进行==hexo==的安装"></a>进行==hexo==的安装</h4><p>随便新建一个==空白==文件夹</p><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820133623906.png" alt="image-20210820133623906"></p><p>右键使用git bash打开命令行</p><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820133709593.png" alt="image-20210820133709593"></p><p>首先需要进行==npm淘宝镜像==</p><p>我在网上查资料的时候别人用的是==cnpm==的方式来搞的 但是不晓得为什么我这里会报错  后来我打开淘宝的镜像网站一看 我尼玛</p><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820135334975.png" alt="image-20210820135334975"></p><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820135349103.png" alt="image-20210820135349103"></p><p>我也不知道是我的问题还是淘宝的问题</p><p>后来我看官方文档 直接输入</p><blockquote><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">npm install -g hexo-cli<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre></blockquote><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820135732053.png" alt="image-20210820135732053"></p><p>安装成功后进行初始化</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo init<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820140221248.png" alt="image-20210820140221248"></p><p>在git bash里面初始化会报错得在当前文件夹的cmd命令下进行初始化命令，不过这波不是因为git的原因是因为GitHub的原因抽疯了 很正常</p><p>然后在cmd里面进行初始化</p><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820140958888.png" alt="image-20210820140958888"></p><p>初始化成功后在git bash中</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo s<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>进行启动就行</p><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820141138876.png" alt="image-20210820141138876"></p><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820141217770.png" alt="image-20210820141217770"></p><p>启动成功</p><h4 id="部署到GitHub中"><a href="#部署到GitHub中" class="headerlink" title="部署到GitHub中"></a>部署到GitHub中</h4><p>首先要注册个GitHub账号 然后新创一个仓库</p><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820141803474.png" alt="image-20210820141803474"></p><p>记得名字最后跟你的用户名一样</p><p>创建好后启动pages服务</p><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820141906169.png" alt="image-20210820141906169"></p><p>安装好插件</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820150246041.png" alt="image-20210820150246041"></p><p>然后打开你的博客根目录打开config配置文件</p><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820141956505.png" alt="image-20210820141956505"></p><p><img src="/2021/08/20/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/image-20210820150316015.png" alt="image-20210820150316015"></p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">deploy:  type: git  repo: https://github.com/yzzx123/yzzx123.github.io.git  branch: master<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>修改成功后保存</p><p>然后</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo d<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>上传就行 </p><p>然后打开GitHub的网页就能看到了</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
